00:01:48.542 --> 00:01:49.210
Alright!

00:01:49.210 --> 00:01:50.260
Saying all that,

00:01:50.260 --> 00:01:53.113
thanks to all of you for continuing to support me,

00:01:53.313 --> 00:01:53.880
soon,

00:01:53.880 --> 00:01:55.415
on the 30th of June,

00:01:55.415 --> 00:01:56.817
